name: Trapped
description: This bloom speaks about toxic relationship. I once was in toxic relationship for 5 years, been gaslighted and pulled back in the name of love. I had never called out for help because I didn't think I was a victim, instead the person made me think I was an abuser. Now, even I can finally step out of the trap, I still cannot meet or talk to the person. I cannot hear the person's name. Please, do not let anyone hurt you in the name of love. It isn't love at all.
